{
  "schemaVersion": "2.0.0",
  "id": "influxdb-data-source-add",
  "title": "Add InfluxDB as a data source",
  "website": {
    "menuTitle": "Add data source",
    "description": "Learn how to navigate Grafana Cloud and add the InfluxDB data source.",
    "weight": 300,
    "step": 4,
    "keywords": ["InfluxDB", "data source", "add", "connections"],
    "cta": { "type": "continue" },
    "side_journeys": {
      "title": "More to explore (optional)",
      "heading": "At this point in your journey, you can explore the following paths:",
      "items": [
        { "title": "Data source management in Grafana", "link": "/docs/grafana/latest/administration/data-source-management/" },
        { "title": "Data source plugins for Grafana", "link": "https://grafana.com/grafana/plugins/data-source-plugins/" }
      ]
    }
  },
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "Grafana includes built-in support for InfluxDB. In this milestone, you add the InfluxDB data source and select Flux as the query language.\n\nLet's walk through the steps together."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "In the navigation menu, navigate to **Connections > Data sources**.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/connections']",
              "requirements": ["navmenu-open"],
              "content": "Click **Connections** in the navigation menu."
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "a[href='/connections/datasources']",
              "requirements": ["navmenu-open"],
              "content": "Click **Data sources**."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "[data-testid='data-testid data-source-add-button']",
          "content": "Click **Add new data source**."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "formfill",
          "reftarget": "input[placeholder='Filter by name or type']",
          "targetvalue": "InfluxDB",
          "content": "In the **Search** field, enter `InfluxDB`."
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "button",
          "reftarget": "InfluxDB",
          "content": "From the search results, click **InfluxDB**."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "In the next milestone, you'll configure the connection details including the URL, organization, bucket, and API token."
    }
  ]
}
